![GCBanner](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a7ee0ee8ef82e9dda0a3489294a2d40d0d7abdf5.png)

This mod adds a variety of creatures to fight (more with each update), with several new bosses, new items and exclusive mechanics.
I'm working on a Wiki to publish the history and details about all the mobs, stay tuned.

This mod was previously released on another platform, so we are skipping the "pre-bugfix" updates and directly releasing the latest fixed version.


    List of normal Mobs (latest update included):

- Psychic Anomaly;
- Knight;
- Skeleton Lich;
- Desert Lurker;
- Fire Spirit;
- Commander Arox;
- Ent;
- Stinger;
- Lost Adventurer;
- Pilim;
- Ghoul;
- Vampire;
- Ghost;
- Feral Pumpkin;
- Bandit;
- Krampus;
- Krampus Elf;
- Nutcracker;
- Living Gift;
- Wild Boar;
- Great Boar;
- Tribal Frog (with alternate);
- Dart Frog (with alternate);
- Shaman Frog;
- Zombie Frog;
- Bullfrog;
- Rebel Frog; 
- Elder Tribal Frog;
- Mudsleeper;
- Dripstone Hermit.


    List of Boss Mobs (latest update included):

- Ancient Samurai;
- Elder Pumpkin;
- Christmas Horror;
- Ascended Frog.


    List of Structures (latest update included):

- Samurai Temple;
- Knight Outpost;
- Bandit Camp;
- Frog Camp;
- Frog Village.



This is a project created by the Blocksmith Creations team.
